  //To set this value, take the Lumas with "calibration standard" written on the inside of it, turn the brightness all the way off, and put it in a room that reads around ~10.20 for "totalLux". Then set the Lumas to be calibrated next to it. adjustVal is Reading_calibrationStandard/Reading_otherLumas
  float adjustVal;
